import sys

n = int(sys.stdin.readline().strip())
k = int(sys.stdin.readline().strip())

def convert(k, n):
    if k == 0:
        return '0'
    s = ''
    while k > 0:
        s = str(k % n) + s
        k /= n
    return s

print convert(k, n)
